    <p><anchor n="T.50.2060.0499c04"/><lb ed="T" n="0499c04"/><persName key="A005400">釋法澄</persName>。<placeName key="PL000000010042">吳郡</placeName>人。少機警善談論。文章書史頗<lb ed="T" n="0499c05"/>皆綜涉。初從<placeName key="PL000000008763">興皇</placeName><persName key="A002918">朗公</persName>講釋三論。至於教<lb ed="T" n="0499c06"/>旨乖競者。皆條理而通暢焉。末聚徒立講<lb ed="T" n="0499c07"/>於<placeName key="PL000000010758">江都開善寺</placeName>。常聽二百餘僧。化洽<placeName key="PL000000008350">吳楚</placeName><lb ed="T" n="0499c08"/>傳譽<placeName key="PL000000010783">淮海</placeName>。負帙相趨日增位席。<persName key="A004413">晉王</persName>置四<lb ed="T" n="0499c09"/>道場。<persName key="A005400">澄</persName>被召入。安時悟物弘<ptr target="fn20"/>導無絕。<date key="j19413501941704" from-iso="0603-02-19" to-iso="0604-02-08">仁<lb ed="T" n="0499c10"/>壽三年</date>。奉<ptr target="fn21"/>令<ptr target="fn22"/><placeName key="PL000000042002">關壤</placeName>居于<placeName key="PL000000042407">日嚴</placeName>。廣流視聽<lb ed="T" n="0499c11"/>憲章新<ptr target="fn23"/>致。披講智論聲望彌重。<placeName key="PL000000042184">京師</placeName>碩學<lb ed="T" n="0499c12"/>咸謁問<persName key="A005400">之</persName>。<persName key="A004413">煬帝</persName>徙駕<placeName key="PL000000023632">東都</placeName>定鼎<placeName key="PL000000023513">伊</placeName><placeName key="PL000000023038">雒</placeName>。從出<lb ed="T" n="0499c13"/>淆右。因疾而終。時年七十餘矣。</p>
